Use the standard library
This is how to prime_fib of n:
   Remember that a is 2
   When n is 1, then:
      The answer is a
   End when
   Remember that b is 3
   When n is 2, then:
      The answer is b
   End when
   Remember that i is 3
   Do this diff of n and 2 times:
      Remember that c is sum of a and b
      Remember that a is b
      Remember that b is c
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is b
Now you know
>>> prime_fib of 1
2
>>> prime_fib of 2
3
>>> prime_fib of 3
5